name: PO Due for Delivery
query:
select po.name, po.docstatus, po.status, po.supplier, po.supplier_name, po.per_received, po.transaction_date,sp.name 
from `tabPurchase Order` po,`tabSupplier` sp where po.supplier_name=sp.name and sp.supplier_group not in ('Transport','Services') and po.status NOT IN ('Draft', 'Cancelled') and po.per_received=0;
